    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and I\u2019m so excited for it to find a new home! It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in great shape for all your daily adventures. It runs beautifully and has been well-loved, making it the perfect companion for road trips or just zipping around town. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready to go, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great home!",
      "price": 32500.0,
