    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with comfort. The exterior retains its original luster, showing only minor road-surface peppering on the front bumper and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear passenger door. Inside, the cabin is a testament to careful ownership; the leather seating is plush and intact, with only light softening of the driver-side bolster. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the intuitive infotainment system, operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs quiet and strong, backed by a comprehensive service history. The transmission provides smooth, seamless shifts, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. Recently fitted with premium tires and having just undergone a full fluid service, this car is mechanically sound and aesthetically pleasing\u2014perfect for someone seeking a premium experience without the new-car price tag.",
